  <?dbhtml dir="actionWait"?>
  <title>Wait</title>
  
  <para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Sometimes it is necessary to wait for a period of time before continuing.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Use this action to tell the AUT Agent to wait for a given amount of time before continuing with the next Test Step.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          There are also actions to wait for a window and a component. If you are waiting for a component, or a window, use the actions specific to these events.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Parameters:
          
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="millisecs"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>
</section>